biography:
An invitation to be #movedbynature 
«Nature is the best perfumer, all you have to do is draw inspiration from it» Issey Miyake
Discover our website:

latestIgtvVideos.caption:
This Summer, let L'Eau d'Issey and L’Eau d’Issey pour Homme take you on an olfactory travel. Enjoy a summer getaway through the Mediterranean with L'Eau d'Issey and L’Eau d’Issey pour Homme by Kevin Lucbert.
#isseymiyakeparfums #olfactorytravel #movedbynature #fragrance

On Mother’s Day, offer a world of poetry and emotion. Enjoy in L’Eau d’Issey the aquatic floral freshness of a fragrance as clear as spring water. Continue your journey through nature with the solar and enveloping trail of a drop d’Issey.
#isseymiyakeparfums #adropdissey #surprisedbynature #movedbynature #fragrance #mothersday

Add a touch of poetry to your everyday with a drop d’Issey.
#isseymiyakeparfums #adropdissey #surprisedbynature #fragrance

latestIgtvVideos.title: a drop d’Issey by the bottle designer Todd Bracher
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Meet the designer Todd Bracher, who broke the codes to design the unprecedented drop-shaped bottle of a drop d'Issey. His vision ? To combine the simplicity of a perfect, poetic shape with the deliberately tactile facet of the bottle in a single piece.
#isseymiyakeparfums #adropdissey #surprisedbynature #fragrance

latestIgtvVideos.title: a drop d’Issey by the perfumer Ane Ayo
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
“To reveal that which is invisible to the naked eye, to craft every detail of the fragrance, as if to conceal surprises at its heart.” Discover the vision of perfumer Ane Ayo, who captured for the first time for Issey Miyake fragrances, the hidden beauty of lilac to reveal it in a drop d'Issey. See how the round-structured enveloping fragrance echoes the drop-shaped bottle...
#isseymiyakeparfums #adropdissey #surprisedbynature #fragrance
